name: 64 Trump Collection: Alice’s Exciting Trip to Trump World
overview:
64 Trump Collection: Alice no Waku Waku Trump World (64 Trump Collection - Alice’s Exciting Trip to Trump World) is a card game based on Alice in Wonderland.

The game was not received well in English speaking territories. N64 Magazine described the game as “an unfathomable Alice in Wonderland-themed card game” which was deemed “a real Lenny Bennett of a game”.
